snippet.title: Seals of the Bygone Early Access Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Class based platformer roguelike! Inspired by games like Risk of Rain and Caveblazers. Void monsters sealed away for eons are awakening across the land! Pick a Sealer and put an end to the chaos! Do you have what it takes to survive?

Releases in Early Access on March 13, 2020.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1093790/Seals_of_the_Bygone
rologfos Twitter: https://twitter.com/rologfos
